\sum_{n=0}^\infty n(x-9)^n=\sum_{n=1}^\infty n(x-9)^n=(x-9)\sum_{n=1}^\infty n(x-9)^{n-1}
\sum_{n=1}^\infty (x-9)^{n}
\sum_{n=1}^\infty (x-9)^{n}=-\frac{x-9}{x-10}
\sum_{n=0}^\infty n(x-9)^n=\frac{x-9}{(x-10)^2}
